{"tid":301368,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"忍界大戰都完咗十鳩幾年-一諗起帶人都覺得好撚慘","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T23:43:02.000Z","uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86357ba9b6c9d7517a95740e5c7afb913e879f03","tid":301368,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"一心做個好人<br />\n點知就畀個祖先冼鑊金<br />\n<br />\n如果野原凜無死喺帶人眼前<br />\n話跟返去木葉就一天都光曬<br />\n<br />\n長門三個唔洗畀人利用<br />\n九尾唔會放出黎<br />\n內輪一族未必會叛變<br />\n就算會都唔洗靠鼬太知一個殺全家去擋<br />\n<br />\n到最後仲要良心發現<br />\n總算做返做好人咁死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係而家班細路本教科書都唔知會點寫佢....<br />\n咁大個污點,可能連提都唔提下<br />\n<br />\n明明佢條暗線貫穿曬第三次同第四次忍界大戰<br />\n但官方紀錄好可能就只係寫佢喺第三次忍界大戰KIA<br />\n<br />\n反而佢老襟平步青雲<br />\n都叫退休嘆下世界<br />\n<br />\n內輪帶人仲喺忍界歷史上盪失緊路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd52b737e6de8bb6da9860dcc50b1f45a3e7b587","tid":301368,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"唔通你想教科書寫帶土引發第四次忍界大戰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而事實上帶土就算係比人利用<br />\n最後做返好人都唔會抵消到佢既罪過<br />\n你諗下佢殺左幾多人，寧次、四代<br />\n講真，木葉唔唱衰佢已經比曬面啦"},{"pid":"8281e6830aee0578